Serial Reader Service
=================================

A simple C# .NET Windows Service that reads values from a
serial device and forwards them any TCP clients connecting to it.

Released under the GNU General Public License, Version 3

TCP Server code based on code by Marc Clifton from 
http://www.codeproject.com/KB/IP/SimplestTcpServer.aspx
released under The Code Project Open License (CPOL).

(c) 2011 Andrei Sosnin
